Kevin Mackey, Cleveland State University basketball coach, was arrested accused 
of drunken driving charge and a female companion was charged with heroin 
possession, police said. 
</P>
<P>
The name of Mackey's companion wasn't immediately released by police. Mackey's 
arrest came two days after he signed a two-year contract to coach Cleveland 
State through the 1991-92 season. His seven-year record with the Vikings is 
144-67. 
</P>
