ground. Another witness reported hearing two shots. The thief fled the scene in 
the cab, carrying the gun, Robinson said.. 
</P>
<P>
Police do not know if the man robbed Tufford, Robinson said. 
</P>
<P>
The thief was described as white, in his early 30s, with long blond hair. 
</P>
<P>
The stolen Yellow Cab, a 1987 Chevrolet Celebrity, is No. 861. 
</P>
<P>
Police ask anyone with information about the case to call 235-TIPS. A $1,000 
reward is available for information leading to an arrest in the case. 
</P>
