HEALTH; FOOD CONTAMINATION AND POISONING; MILK; HANFORD NUCLEAR POWER PLANT; 
THYROID; CANCER; RADIOACTIVE MATERIALS; NUCLEAR SAFETY; AIR POLLUTION -- 
WASHINGTON (STATE); UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT; GOVERNMENT MISCONDUCT 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
