MAYORS; SHANGHAI (CHINA) -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; CHINA -- GOVERNMENT; 
COMMUNIST PARTY (CHINA); DEMONSTRATIONS -- CHINA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
