<P>
CALIFORNIA -- BUDGET; CALIFORNIA -- FINANCES; WELFARE PROGRAMS -- CALIFORNIA; 
GOVERNMENT SPENDING; CALIFORNIA -- GOVERNMENT EMPLOYEES -- WAGES AND SALARIES; 
STATE AID 
</P>
