<P>
CALIFORNIA -- ELECTIONS -- 1990; POLITICAL CANDIDATES; HUNTINGTON BEACH (CA) -- 
ELECTIONS; BANNISTER, WES; CALIFORNIA STATE INSURANCE COMMISSIONER; HUNTINGTON 
BEACH CITY COUNCIL 
</P>
